title: Kordis Strong Tie Handle Pedal Bin Liners - 8 x 30 Bags. 25L White Plastic Bin Bag Liners For Bedroom, Bathroom, Office, Mini Trash Can & Small Bins. 240 Unscented Garbage Bags (53 x 70cm)
features: PEDAL BIN LINERS: The Kordis Pedal Bin Liners are the perfect waste solution for any small bin in your home. Each pack includes 8 rolls, and each roll consists of 30 liners, a total of 240 bags, which work out at just 5.8p per liner. With our tie-handle pedal bin liners, getting rid of the trash will be a breeze.

TIE HANDLES: These small bin liners are designed with simple tie handles, which are easy to lift and carry, and allows a convenient, efficient use. The large handles are strong, ensuring no tears or split bags, aided by the heavy duty leak proof resistant base.

STRENGTH WITH LESS PLASTIC: Our 25L bin bags are made with high performance polythene, using less material to achieve the same strength and durability as other thicker products, saving on raw plastic materials, whilst remaining extra strong and light weight.

MULTIPURPOSE: These rubbish bin liners are ideal for many small bins, such as: bathroom bin, bedroom vanity bin, office trash can, nursery nappy bin, sanitary bin, and any other pedal bin in your home.

SPECIFICATIONS: Bag Measurements - Rim 53cm, 70cm long including tie handles. Capacity - 25 litres. Colour - White. Material - Polythene. Pack Size - 8 x 30 bags, 240 count total. Kordis offer a wide range of disposal solutions, including - Pedal bin liners, swing bin liners, refuse sacks, food and freezer bags, and garden waste bags.
